data.text:
Aosta, Aosta Valley, Italy

Latitude and longitude coordinates are: 45.734955, 7.313076.

Aosta is a large town situated in Aosta Valley in north western Italy, about 70 miles north of Torino. The area is bordering with France and the population of the town and the district is dominantly bilingual, speaking both Italian and French. Aosta is a beautiful old historic town, with the population close to 35,000 people. It can be reached by Northern Highway 26. It is a tourist destination and those who visit the town can observe its interesting lifestyle, visit the historic places and take a small tour to the famous Mont Blanc mountain situated nearby.
